  "texts": [
    "Enabling the TL technique can also increase the AUC in LQ videos by 0.8 for the CelebDF dataset when assessing AUC.",
    "Extensive experiments show that the BFLDL method may deliver excellent results on a variety of datasets.",
    "In general, a model trained with TL will outperform a model trained from scratch (without TL).",
    "This is because TL enables the model to apply information and skills learned from a big, general-purpose dataset, such as ImageNet, to the new task.",
    "When a model is trained from scratch, it begins with random weights and must learn everything about the task from the provided data."
